# .dockerignore — keeps the build context small and the image clean.
# Every entry below is excluded from the context sent to the Docker daemon.
# A smaller context means faster builds and no accidental leakage of local
# artifacts into image layers.

# --- Application/npm generated output ---------------------------------------

# node_modules: installed fresh inside the image with `npm ci`. Copying the
# host's modules would bloat the context and risk shipping OS-specific native
# binaries (e.g. pg) built for the host instead of the Alpine container.
node_modules

# dist: the compiled output is produced inside the builder stage by
# `npm run build`. Any local copy is stale and must not override the build.
dist

# *.tsbuildinfo: TypeScript incremental build cache, only meaningful on the
# host. Rebuilt inside the image; never needed at runtime.
*.tsbuildinfo

# coverage: Jest test-coverage reports. A local artifact, useless in the image.
coverage

# --- Infrastructure (not part of the runnable service) ----------------------

# cdk + cdk.out: AWS CDK infrastructure project and its synthesized output.
# This deploys the service to Lambda; it is not needed to RUN the container and
# carries its own large node_modules. Excluding it greatly shrinks the context.
cdk
cdk.out

# --- Tests and dev-only config ----------------------------------------------

# test: e2e test suite — not executed in the production image.
test

# Linter/formatter configs: used only during development, not at runtime.
.eslintrc.js
.prettierrc

# --- Version control & docs -------------------------------------------------

# .git: full repository history. Large and irrelevant to the running app.
.git
.gitignore

# Documentation and local helper assets — not part of the service.
README.md
DEVELOPMENT_PLAN.md
pics
get-token.sh

# --- Secrets / environment --------------------------------------------------

# env.example and any local .env files: configuration is injected at runtime
# via environment variables, never baked into the image.
env.example
.env
*.local

# --- Editor / OS noise ------------------------------------------------------

.vscode
.idea
.DS_Store
npm-debug.log*
Dockerfile
.dockerignore
